Serve your wino friends in style, with this beautiful gold serving tray featuring the phrase &quot;Live, Love, Wine&quot;. Both the words and the wine stain ring are cut entirely from reclaimed wine bottle labels and sealed with a layer of epoxy-resin for durability and preservation. The bottom of the tray is completely waterproof and heat-resistant, so it can withstand hard use without worry of damaging the art below.

Dimensions: L 19&quot; x W 13&quot; x H 1.5&quot;

*Message seller for custom projects.
